## Tool Tips

**PTY** (when enabled): Load the `pty` skill when working with background processes.

**GitHub PR Inline Comments**: Load the `gh-pr-inline` skill when posting inline comments on PRs or responding to review feedback. When addressing feedback: resolve threads you fixed (no reply needed), reply only to threads you're not addressing.
